text: Emmaculate Chemtai (born 14 October 1993) is a Kenyan volleyball player. She is part of the Kenya women's national volleyball team. She participated in the 2018 World Championship and 2019 FIVB Women's World Cup. She was chosen to represent Kenya at the 2020 Summer Olympics. == Clubs == * 2017-2018 Kenya Prisons == References == Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Kenyan volleyball players
